pravati]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：de（加强）+prav（坏）+ity→变坏→堕落"},{"type":"entry","text":"irk","headword":"irk"},{"type":"text","text":".使苦恼，使厌烦（to annoy;disgust)"},{"type":"text","text":"[3:rk]"},{"type":"text","text":"园发音记忆：“饿渴”→又饿又渴，当然很苦恼→使苦恼"},{"type":"entry","text":"dilapidate","headword":"dilapidate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. (使)荒度， (使)毁坏(to bring into a condition of decay or partial ruin)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'laprdert]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：di（二）+lapid（石头）+ate→石基倒場成为两半→（使）荒废，（使）毁坏"},{"type":"entry","text":"nascent","headword":"nascent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 初生的, 萌芽的(beginning to exist or develop)"},{"type":"text","text":"[naesnt]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：nasc(出生）+ent→刚出生的→初生的"},{"type":"entry","text":"foolproof","headword":"foolproof"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 极易懂的，十分简单的(so simple, well designed as not to be mishandled)"},{"type":"text","text":"['fu:lpru:f]"},{"type":"text","text":"组合词：fool（笨蛋）+proof（防的）→以防受限于人的无能而做得尤其简单好用"},{"type":"text","text":"→人人都会操作的→极易懂的"},{"type":"entry","text":"ravel","headword":"ravel"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使纠缠，纠结(to become twisted and knotted)：拆开，拆散(to unravel)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ravl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"entangle","headword":"entangle"},{"type":"entry","text":"bumptious","headword":"bumptious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.傲慢的，自夸的(crudely or loudly assertive)"},{"type":"text","text":"['bampfas]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：bump（碰撞）+tious→顶撞人→做慢的"},{"type":"entry","text":"cameo","headword":"cameo"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.刻有浮雕的宝石（jewel carved inrelief)：生动刻画：（演员）出演"},{"type":"text","text":"['kaemiau]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：came（来）+0→来哦→演员来哦→出演"},{"type":"entry","text":"vile","headword":"vile"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.恶劣的，卑都的，道德败坏的(morally despicable or abhorrent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[varl]"},{"type":"text","text":"abject, contemptible, filthy, loathsome"},{"type":"entry","text":"bracing","headword":"bracing"},{"type":"defini