rone);休息的(resting)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'kAmbant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（向后）+cumb（躺）+ent→斜靠的"},{"type":"entry","text":"pundit","headword":"pundit"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 权威人土，专家(one who gives opinions in an authoritative manner)"},{"type":"text","text":"('pandrt]"},{"type":"text","text":"园pandit（n.学者，专家）变体"},{"type":"entry","text":"sentinel","headword":"sentinel"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.哨兵，岗明(sentry, lookout)"},{"type":"text","text":"['sentinl]"},{"type":"text","text":"stand sentinel 站岗，守卫"},{"type":"entry","text":"fitful","headword":"fitful"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj间歇的，不规则的"},{"type":"text","text":"['frtfl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：fit（一阵）+ful（充满-的）→一阵阵的→间歇的"},{"type":"entry","text":"condole","headword":"condole"},{"type":"text","text":"同情，哀悼（to express sympathy;commiserate）"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'daul]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：con（共同）+dole（悲伤）→一起悲伤→哀悼"},{"type":"entry","text":"lamentable","headword":"lamentable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj令人惋惜的，悔恨的（expressing grief)"},{"type":"text","text":"[la'mentabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自lament（n/v.悔恨；悲叹）"},{"type":"entry","text":"excruciate","headword":"excruciate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 施酷刑：折据(to subject to intense mental distress)"},{"type":"text","text":"[1k'skru:fiert]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：ex+cruci（看作crude，残忍的）+ate→给人施酷刑是很残忍的→施酷刑"},{"type":"entry","text":"contumacious","headword":"contumacious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 违抗的，不服从的(unreasonably disobedient, esp. to an order made by a"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:ntu'merfas]"},{"type":"text","text":"court)"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：con（强调）+tum（肿胀；骄做）+acious（---的）→坚持自己的骄做，不受"},{"type":"text","text":"欺压→违抗的，不服从的"},{"type":"entry","text":"oath","headword":"oath"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 管言(a formal promise to fulfill a pledige, especially one made in a court of"},{"type":"text","text":"[aue]"},{"type":"text","text":"law)：咒骂，退咒(swearword)"},{"type":"entry","text":"m