inition","text":"v. 量 -口径(to determine the calibre of) : 校ll(to adjust precisely)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kaelrbrert]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自calibre（n.口径）"},{"type":"entry","text":"sunder","headword":"sunder"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 分, 分离(to separate by violence or by intervening time or space)"},{"type":"text","text":"['sAndar]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆发音记忆：“散的”→分离"},{"type":"entry","text":"rustle","headword":"rustle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 发出沙沙声(to make slight sounds like silk moving or being rubbed together)"},{"type":"text","text":"['rAsI]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：可能来自rush（n.匆促）"},{"type":"entry","text":"tweak","headword":"tweak"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.扭，拧，挑(to pinch and pull with a sudden jerk and twist)：调节，微调(to"},{"type":"text","text":"[twi:k]"},{"type":"text","text":"make usually small adjustments in or to)"},{"type":"entry","text":"ardent","headword":"ardent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 热心的,热烈的(intensely enthusiastic or devoted; passionate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:rdnt]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ard（热）+ent→热心的，热烈的"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.呕吐(to vomit);大量喷出(to come forth in a flood or gush)"},{"type":"entry","text":"spew","headword":"spew"},{"type":"text","text":"[spju:]"},{"type":"entry","text":"narcissism","headword":"narcissism"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.自恋，自盈(inordinate fascination with oneself)"},{"type":"text","text":"['na:rsisizam]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自Narcissus，希腊神话中的美少年，因过于爱恋自己水中的影子而溺水身"},{"type":"text","text":"亡，化为水仙花（narcissus）"},{"type":"entry","text":"peruse","headword":"peruse"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 细读，精读(to read sth. in a careful way)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa'ru:z]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：per（始终）+us（用）+e→反复用→细读，精读"},{"type":"entry","text":"daft","headword":"daft"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj傻的，愚套的（silly, foolish)"},{"type":"text","text":"[daeft]"},{"type":"entry","text":"redoubtable","headword":"redoubtable"},{"type":"definition","text":"